   <abstract>Title translates as "Wars of the Dark Forces", written by Nikolai Evgen'evich Markov. He was the influential leader of the Kursk branch of the Union of the Russian People and Union of Michael the Archangel, chauvinist, and member of the anti-Semitic organization, the Black Hundreds. This book depicts Jews as a "malevolent race" and calls for the unmasking of the Jewish conspiracy. The Beilis trial is discussed in the displayed chapter.</abstract>
